### ================================================
### 테스트 데이터 준비
### ================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@userId = testuser01

### ================================================
### 1. 회원 가입
### ================================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users/join
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "memberId": "testuser01",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "birthDate": "1990-01-01",
  "gender": "MALE"
}

### ================================================
### 2. 포인트 충전 (10,000원)
### ================================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/points/charge
X-USER-ID: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 10000
}

### ================================================
### 3. 포인트 충전 (50,000원 추가)
### ================================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/points/charge
X-USER-ID: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 50000
}

### ================================================
### 4. 포인트 조회
### ================================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/points
X-USER-ID: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### ================================================
### 5. 상품 목록 조회
### ================================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products?page=0&size=20
Content-Type: application/json

### ================================================
### 6. 상품 상세 조회
### ================================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

